00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,600
Here's what science actually says about blood pressure basics.

2
00:00:03,600 --> 00:00:07,600
Blood pressure measures the force of blood against your arteries.

3
00:00:07,600 --> 00:00:12,000
High blood pressure can lead to serious health issues—think heart attacks.

4
00:00:12,000 --> 00:00:16,000
Studies show that reducing salt intake significantly lowers blood pressure.

5
00:00:16,000 --> 00:00:19,600
Managing stress and regular exercise also play crucial roles.

6
00:00:19,600 --> 00:00:21,600
Curious about your blood pressure?

7
00:00:21,600 --> 00:00:23,600
Check with a doctor today!
